dcterms:description: The FEDas Greenbook data comprises all numerical and text data captured in the 145 Greenbooks released from 1990 to 2013, including numerical estimates of economic indicators and forecasts for various time horizons, along with accompanying text passages that provide context for the forecasts.
dcterms:title: FEDas Greenbook data

dcterms:description: The public speeches of central bankers comprise textual transcripts of over 3000 speeches given by central bankers over the time span from 1993 to 2013, used to estimate monetary policy signals and dispersion indices.
dcterms:title: Public speeches of central bankers
